    "description": {
      "value": "<p>With a single shout, the shaman causes one target creature within 30 feet to become shaken for 1 round. A successful Will saving throw negates this effect.</p>\n<p>At 8th level, she makes the target frightened instead.</p>\n<p>At 16th level, she makes it panicked instead. This is a mind-affecting fear effect.</p>\n<p>A creature affected by this hex cannot be affected by it again for 24 hours.</p>"
